                <h4 id="welcome-to-my-homepage"><center>Welcome to my homepage!</center></h4>

<p><img class="profile-picture" src="website.jpg" style="width: 90px;" /></p>

<p>I am a PhD student in the <a href="http://www.cs.uic.edu/">Department of Computer Science</a> at the <a href="http://www.uic.edu/">University of Illinois at Chicago</a>, working with my advisor Professor <a href="https://www.cs.uic.edu/~ckanich/">Chris Kanich</a>. I received my BS in Computer Science from Sharif University of Technology, Iran.</p>

<h3 id="research-interest">Research Interest</h3>

<p>My research areas generally lie in security and privacy. My current research projects mainly focus on Machine Learning applications in security and privacy.</p>

<h3 id="academic-experience">Academic Experiences</h3>

<ul>
  <li>Research Assistant, <a href="https://www.cs.uic.edu/bin/view/Bits/WebHome">BITS Networked Systems Laboratory</a>, University of Illinois at Chicago: Fall 2015 - Present</li>
  <li>Teaching Assistant, Intro to Data Science (CS491), University of Illinois at Chicago: Spring 2016</li>
  <li>Teaching Assistant, Computer Organization (CS261), University of Illinois at Chicago: Fall 2014, Spring 2015, Fall 2015</li>
  <li>Teaching Assistant, Intro to Computer Networking, Sharif University of Technology: Fall 2013</li>
</ul>

<h3 id="work-experience">Work Experience</h3>

<ul>
  <li>Data Scientist Intern at Target: June 2017 - August 2017 <br> Exploring a novel idea to be used towards improving shopping check out process and recommender systems using machine learning methods (resulted in a <strong>filed patent</strong>).</li>
</ul>


<h3 id="publications">Publications</h3>

<p>Sara Amini, Vahid Noroozi, Sara Bahaadini, Philip S. Yu, Chris Kanich, "<strong>DeepFP: A Deep Learning Framework For User Fingerprinting via Mobile Motion Sensors,</strong>" <em>BigData,</em> 2018.<a href="Amini_bigdata18CV.pdf" download>[PDF]</a></p>

<p> Sara Amini, Vahid Noroozi, Amit Pande, Satyajit Gupte, Philip S. Yu, Chris Kanich, "<strong>DeepAuth: A Framework for Continuous User Re-authentication in Mobile Apps,</strong>" <em>CIKM,</em> 2018. <a href="amini_CIKM18_deepAuth.pdf" download>[PDF]</a></p>

<p> Sara Amini, Nasim Mobasheri, Chris Kanich, Vahid Balali, "<strong>Forum vs. Social Network: What is the best for company and customers?,</strong>‚Äù <em>WDSI,</em> 2018. </p>

<p> Sara Amini and Chris Kanich, "<strong>Characterizing the Impact of Malware Infections and Remediation Attempts Through Support Forum Analysis,</strong>" <em>eCrime,</em> 2017. <a href="amini2017characterizing.pdf" download>[PDF]</a></p>

<h3 id="patents">Patents</h3>

<p> Amit Pande, Sara Amini, Satyajit Gupte, "<strong>Continuous Guest Re-Authentication System,</strong>" <em>US Patent 15/990,572 filed,</em> 2018.</p>

